services:
AGM Renovations offers Complete basement and Bathroom renovations packages from the professional design through the professional cleaning including:

Drywall- We employ only professional drywall installers and our goal is deliver complete satisfaction to each and every client with the quality of our workmanship and our prompt, reliable service.
    
Taping- Our drywall taping techniques will bring a high quality smooth finish, with a level of excellence you will take pride in.

Painting- We include all wall priming, painting of ceilings, baseboards, casing, crown and cove moldings into our basement construction packages
    
High Grade Laminate Flooring- is standard in our basement renovations packages.

Tiling- Shower, bathroom, or kitchenette tiling will be done by professional tile installers who are employed directly by AGM. A 2 year unlimited warranty is provided to you standard when you finish your basement with AGM
   
Plumbing- Our licensed plumbers will ensure that no problem is left unsolved and you can be sure that any drain or other plumbing defects left by the original house builder will be fixed effectively.

Electrical- We are committed to providing fully licensed electrician service as part of our standard package. Should you ever require an electrical certificate when you decide to sell your property, we will be happy to provide it to you

profile:
Amell's Better Cabinetry Design provides kitchen cabinet refacing with unparalleled quality and appearance here in the Niagara Region. We can design or reface your entire kitchen and bath with elegance that surpasses our competitors design and quality.  With over 40 years of kitchen design and experience, we offer new or reface cabinetry. Cabinetry for all spaces, kitchens, bathrooms, mud rooms or bedrooms, the possibilities are endless. 

About US: We are a home-based business located in the small quiet city of Welland within the Niagara Region. We primarily service the Niagara Region from Fort Erie and up to Vineland and Grimsby. Started in the 1980's by Mike Amell, with well over 20 years of experience in the kitchen industry. Mike takes pride in his companies speciality of refacing along with the ability to provide custom cabinets and kitchen designs also. We at A.B.C Designs have the ability of refacing existing cabinetry and/or providing custom cabinets to help our customers achieve the best kitchen design based on expectation and budget. If refacing is not doable we are equipped to provide our customers with new custom cabinets also. 

We're looking forward to working with you on your next project. Contact us today to schedule an appointment.

Welcome to Rosewood Custom Cabinetry
We are a custom cabinetry & design company, specializing in custom kitchens.
